# Cloud Security Analyzer with AI

An AI-powered AWS Cloud Security Analyzer built with Flask, Boto3, Bootstrap, and Ollama.

## Features

- AWS Security Group Scanner
- IAM Scanner
- AI Security Assessment (Ollama)
- Dashboard
- Charts
- PDF Report
- Excel Report

## Requirements

- Python 3
- AWS CLI
- Ollama

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Abhiraj2603/cloud-security-analyzer.git

cd cloud-security-analyzer

chmod +x *.sh

./install.sh
```

## Start Application

```bash
./start.sh
```

## Stop Application

```bash
./stop.sh
```

## Open

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

## AWS Authentication

Configure credentials:

```bash
aws configure
```

or use an EC2 IAM Role.

## AI

Uses the local Ollama model:

```
llama3.2
```
